        {
            "id": 5980055,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 費城半導體大漲1.01%，報4980.95點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間14日09:33，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>上漲49.6點（或1.01%），暫報4980.95點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+14.38%</li><li>近 1 月：+23.56%</li><li>近 3 月：-4.36%</li><li>近 6 月：-1.5%</li><li>今年以來：-0.98%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>成分股以超微半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMD-US</a>)領漲。超微半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMD-US</a>)上漲7.99%；安謀控股公司(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ARM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ARM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ARM-US</a>)上漲3.77%；輝達(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>)上漲3.12%；Onto Innovation Inc.(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ONTO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ONTO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ONTO-US</a>)上漲2.34%；英特格(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ENTG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ENTG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ENTG-US</a>)上漲1.32%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對疲軟，英特爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)下跌1.06%；德州儀器(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TXN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TXN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TXN-US</a>)下跌0.89%；超捷國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MCHP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MCHP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MCHP-US</a>)下跌0.88%；思佳訊半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SWKS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SWKS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SWKS-US</a>)下跌0.4%；恩智浦半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NXPI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NXPI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NXPI-US</a>)下跌0.19%。</p></section></main>",
